1.title: Un show-room, un gobierno en funciones y un mariquita negador
1.plot: Vicente's presidential term ends, leaving a power vacuum that nobody wants to occupy. The incipient friendship of Lola and Yolanda provokes jealousy to Javi and Coque studies the way to break with Nines without her suffering.

2.title: Una asexual, unas amiguis y un fantasma goloso
2.plot: Bruno begins an affair with Maite, who will be threatened by the traumas of his divorce and by his ignorance in the flirt's market. Meanwhile, Amador, unable to overcome his love break with Yolanda, will turn his life and Teodoro's into a hell.

3.title: Una sugarbaby, un filet muñón y un diógenes exprés
3.plot: Yoli no longer loves Amador, but he doesn't want to lose her altogether and intends to make her jealous of a young university student. Meanwhile, Antonio convinces Enrique to set up a restaurant, which leads them to hire a "reputed" chef.

4.title: Una conserja, un romance imposible y un cuesco traicionero
4.plot: Fermin, who urgently needs a janitor just hiring Clara, Menchu's niece. Chusa takes advantage of her pregnancy to disregard her obligations. And Alba starts dating in secret with Enrique.

5.title: Una novia virtual, una Pretty Chacha y un mamoneo confuso
5.plot: The new clandestine relationship maintained by Teodoro and Yoli threatens to disturb Montepinar. Amelia, Bruno's conservative mother, wants to concoct her future grandchild. And Enrique will continue to suffer for hiding his relationship with Alba.

6.title: Un referente paterno, una maldición rumana y la caza del fornicador del trastero
6.plot: Vicente is so depressed by Clarita's departure. Amador will be named president and will decide to discover which neighbors use the storage. Recio wants to get closer to her daughter to improve their relationship, which will hinder her love relationship.

7.title: Una hipoteca bienestar, dos inventores frustrados y una marisquería-cabaret
7.plot: Javier is worried about the new relationship of his father Vicente. Alba turns to refloat Enrique's business while Antonio sets up a restaurant to compete with them. In addition, Menchu will begin to fantasize with Teo, the boyfriend of his daughter Yoli.

8.title: Un suegro lapa, una maruja liberada y una epidemia youtuber
8.plot: Fermin tries to recover Menchu. Javi, after being unemployed, discovers that "chicken' eyes" is a computer genius. Alba moves with Enrique to throw Anotino. Meanwhile, the whole community will want to become the biggest youtuber phenomenon of the moment.

9.title: Un chupito castrador, un mozo leal y sumiso y dos estrategas del amor
9.plot: Amador gets a new girlfriend who does not finish convincing him. Alba is still trying to make life as a couple with Enrique; while Antonio tries to recover his Empire. The relationship between Vicente and Fermin keeps getting closer.

10.title: Un bypass, un conserje titulado y un mayorista zulú
10.plot: Fermin tries to get Vicente out of the depression. Antonio, in his attempt to be a better person, hires Berta's new boyfriend. While the entire community is awaiting Patricio, the new concierge, who seems to be hiding something from them.

11.title: Un depredador africano, una muñequita rusa y una noche chochete-free
11.plot: Amador seems to have finally found a new love. Fermin and Antonoi travel to Russia, each for a different reason. Teodoro sees how his relationship with Yoli is broken by a night of partying with his brother.

12.title: Un chochete pasajero, una lesbiana con mochila y el padre Piruelas
12.plot: The new girlfriend of Maite, Daphne is delighted with her, but it is not expected that the children of Maite and her ex-husband Amador will appear in their house, in which they will stay while they travel to London. The brother of Teodoro and Amador, Rogelio appears, nobody knows why.

13.title: Un culebrón interracial, una detención ilegal y el palacete del Conde Manfredzum Neuenthurn von der Pfordten
13.plot: Vicente and Fermín finally give the "I do", although it will cost to get room for the wedding. Half of the Community is hooked on the soap opera of the Recios house, which they follow by webcams. Amador and Maite are sued by their children.
